'''《马来西亚联邦政府宪报》'''（{{lang-en|Federal Government Gazette}}；{{lang-ms|Warta Kerajaan Persekutuan}}）是[[马来西亚联邦政府|马来西亚联邦政府]]发布公告、启事和法律等的官方出版物。<ref>{{cite|url=https://www.lawteacher.net/free-law-essays/administrative-law/malaysia-procedure-for-enactment-law-essays.php|title=Malaysia Procedure for Enactment of an Act|publisher=LawTeacher|language=en}}</ref>联邦政府宪报由[[马来西亚总检察长|马来西亚总检察署]]（Attorney-General's Chambers，AGC）发布，并由马来西亚国家印刷有限公司（PNMB）印刷。<ref>{{cite|url=http://www.federalgazette.agc.gov.my/eng_main/main_faq.php|title=Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)
|publisher=Federal Government Gazette (Malaysia)|language=en}}</ref>任何在[[马来西亚国会|马来西亚国会]]通过和[[最高元首|最高元首]]御准的联邦法律，都需要在联邦政府宪报上发布刊登方能生效。<ref>{{cite|url=http://mobile.cljlaw.com/?page=legislationoverview|title=Legislation: An Overview|language=en|publisher=CLJ Legal Network Malaysia}}</ref><ref>[http://www.agc.gov.my/agcportal/uploads/files/Publications/FC/Federal%20Consti%20(BI%20text).pdf Federal Constitution of Malaysia] {{Wayback|url=http://www.agc.gov.my/agcportal/uploads/files/Publications/FC/Federal%20Consti%20(BI%20text).pdf |date=20171010090526 }}, [[马来西亚总检察长|Attorney-General]]'s Chambers (Malaysia) {{en}}</ref>

